title:Start
---
<<char_clear_all>>
<<bg_load "CityStreetsDay">>
Voice: The following is a test of all major functions of Magic Connect's scene editor.
Voice: All functions, stand by.
<<vfx_fg_blackout 1.0>>
<<wait_anim>>
Voice: Black out nominal.
<<vfx_fg_fadein 1.0>>
<<wait_anim>>
Voice: Fade in nominal.
<<bg_switch "CityStreetsNight" 1.0>>
<<wait_anim>>
Voice: Background switch nominal.
<<char_add "Lana" "LanaElenore" Center>>
<<char_show Lana 1.0>>
Lana: Hey! What the--
Voice: Character show nominal.
Lana: What's going on?
<<char_move Lana OffscreenLeft 750.0 smoothLerp>>
Lana: Hey!
<<char_move Lana OffscreenRight 750.0 smoothLerp>>
Lana: Woah!
<<char_move Lana Center 750.0 smoothLerp>>
Voice: Character move nominal.
<<char_dim Lana 1.0>>
Lana: --!
Lana: I can't see!
<<char_undim Lana 1.0>>
Lana: Cut it out!
Voice: Character dimming nominal.
<<char_hide Lana 1.0>>
<<wait_anim>>
<<char_clear Lana>>
Voice: Character cleared from memory.
Voice: All major functions nominal.
Voice: This concludes our test.
Voice: Shutting down. 
<<char_clear_all>>
<<wait 0.5>>
<<bg_blackout 1.0>>


